(277, 'Climbing Rose \'Joseph\'s Coat\' Starter Plant Perennial Shrub Fragrant Color Changing Yellow Orange Red---Beautiful!!', 'climbing-rose-josephs-coat-starter-plant-perennial-shrub-fragrant-color-changing-yellow-orange-red-beautiful', 'ETSY-0005', 'simple', 9, NULL, 'Roses', 27.90, NULL, 16.74, NULL, 'https://i.etsystatic.com/20088520/r/il/0d6df8/4886107424/il_fullxfull.4886107424_etqs.jpg', 'WE CANNOT SHIP TO THE FOLLOWING STATES DUE TO SHIPPING RESTRICTIONS: CALIFORNIA, OREGON, WASHINGTON, ARIZONA, ALASKA, HAWAII, IDAHO AND NEVADA\n**WE CANNOT SHIP TO P.O. BOXES!!**\nSECOND PICTURE IS A REPRESENTATION OF THE PLANT YOU WILL RECEIVE.\n***ITEMS ARE TAPED IN THE BOX FOR SECURE SHIPPING. PLEASE BE CAREFUL TO REMOVE TAPE FIRST BEFORE REMOVING PLANT(S)***\n\nThis listing is for 1 live starter plant that is 3\" - 6\" tall and growing quickly in a quart pot! If you are looking for a unique Rose, this is it!! It blooms in flushes from Spring to Fall with flowers that change from yellow to scarlet and back to orange and carmine...wow!! This is a tall climber that works great on a trellis, pergola or fence and really puts on a show! Definitely add this one to your Rose collection!!\n\nCommon Name: \'Joseph\'s Coat\' Rose\nBotanical Name: Rosa\nHardiness Zones: 5 - 9\nBloom Time: Spring, Summer, Fall\nSunlight: Full sun\nSoil Requirements: Moist, well drained soil\nMature Size: 8\' to 12\' tall and 3\' to 4\' wide\nBloom Color: Color changes...yellow, orange, red\nDeciduous or Evergreen: Deciduous', '1 live starter plant that is 3\" - 6\" tall and growing quickly in a quart pot! If you are looking for a unique Rose, this is it!! It blooms in flushes from Spring to Fall with flowers that change from yellow to scarlet an...', '[\"Low Maintenance\",\"Cottage Garden\",\"Spring Flowers\",\"Summer Flowers\",\"Fall Flowers\",\"Cut Flowers\",\"Attracts Butterflies\",\"Easy To Grow\",\"Pollinators Love\",\"Showy Flowers\",\"Fragrant Flowers\",\"Courtyard Garden\",\"Climbs An Arbor