(316, 'Climbing Rose \'America\'  1 year Live Plant Salmon Pink Double Flowers Highly Fragrant---Gorgeous!!', 'climbing-rose-america-1-year-live-plant-salmon-pink-double-flowers-highly-fragrant-gorgeous', 'ETSY-0044', 'simple', 9, NULL, 'Roses', 32.90, NULL, 19.74, NULL, 'https://i.etsystatic.com/20088520/r/il/449127/6733669921/il_fullxfull.6733669921_4qq1.jpg', 'WE CANNOT SHIP TO THE FOLLOWING STATES DUE TO SHIPPING RESTRICTIONS: CALIFORNIA, OREGON, WASHINGTON, ARIZONA, ALASKA, HAWAII, IDAHO AND NEVADA\n**WE CANNOT SHIP TO P.O. BOXES!!**\nSECOND PICTURE IS A REPRESENTATION OF THE PLANT YOU WILL RECEIVE.\n***ITEMS ARE TAPED IN THE BOX FOR SECURE SHIPPING. PLEASE BE CAREFUL TO REMOVE TAPE FIRST BEFORE REMOVING PLANT(S)***\n\nThis listing is for 1 live plant that is 8\"- 12\" tall and growing quickly!  This Rose variety can bloom in waves all season long!! In late Spring, it starts the show with salmon/coral colored double blooms that are highly fragrant!! Absolutely stunning when grown on a fence, trellis or pergola!! A definite statement maker in your garden!!\n\n**Not shipped in a pot, but the rootball is placed in a polybag and sealed. This will keep the roots moist!**\n\nCommon Name: \'America\' Climbing Rose\nBotanical Name: Rosa\nHardiness Zones: 6 - 9\nBloom Time: Late Spring\nSunlight: Full sun \nSoil Requirements: Moist, well drained soil\nMature Size: 10\' to 12\' tall and 6\' to 8\' wide\nBloom Color: Salmon pink\nEvergreen or Deciduous: Deciduous', '1 live plant that is 8\"- 12\" tall and growing quickly! This Rose variety can bloom in waves all season long!! In late Spring, it starts the show with salmon/coral colored double blooms that are highly fragrant!! Absolute...', '[\"Showy Flowers\",\"Highly Fragrant\",\"Heirloom Rose\",\"Fast Growing\",\"Climbs A Pergola\",\"Climbs A Trellis\",\"Cut Flowers\",\"Cottage Garden\",\"Easy To Grow\",\"Strong Canes\",\"Long Bloom Time\",\"Double Flowers\",\"Attracts Pollinators\"]', 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 3, 5, 1, 0, 5, '2026-06-24 16:09:08', '2026-06-24 16:09:08');
