(3207, 384, 80, NULL, 5, NULL, 'There\'s nothing like opening up a box that has a brand new beautiful Japanese Maple in it,  well maybe opening up a box that has 5 incredibly beautiful Japanese Maples in it. Meadowlark Gardens are a excellent place to buy these wonderful trees. They have a great selection and the prices are very good. The staff are very friendly and knowledgeable. The trees come exactly as described and always arrive in perfect condition and arrive very fast.', 'description_accuracy', 5, 5, 5, NULL, NULL, '[]', 1, 0, 'approved', '2024-06-19 16:19:40', '2024-06-19 16:19:40'),
