(3214, 398, 80, NULL, 5, NULL, 'MEADOWLARK Gardens is the place to go for your Japanese maple trees! They have great choices for even better prices. The staff are excellent to work with and are very knowledgeable. The shipping is very fast and the trees always arrive in perfect condition.', 'delivery_packaging', 5, 5, 5, NULL, NULL, '[]', 1, 0, 'approved', '2024-06-18 16:19:40', '2024-06-18 16:19:40'),
(3215, 398, 80, NULL, 5, NULL, 'I have received another stunning Japanese maple from Tracy and the gang from Meadowlark Gardens,  the Kasagi Yama is really incredible, it came in excellent condition and arrived very fast. They may not do over a Thousand varieties but they have a lot and you can get it, immediately, instead of having to be put on a list. If you want a great tree at a great price then you arrived.', 'delivery_packaging', 5, 5, 5, NULL, NULL, '[]', 1, 0, 'approved', '2024-06-18 16:19:41', '2024-06-18 16:19:41'),
(3216, 314, 80, NULL, 5, NULL, 'I just received another beautiful Japanese Maple from the Meadowlark Gardens gang. As always it is absolutely gorgeous. It has good size on it and is in excellent condition. They have very nice trees and are reasonably priced. The staff are great to answer any questions you may have and are very knowledgeable. If you are thinking about getting a Japanese Maple then I highly recommend giving them a chance. You won\'t be disappointed. And probably the fastest shipping around.', 'delivery_packaging', 5, 5, 5, NULL, NULL, '[]', 1, 0, 'approved', '2024-06-18 16:19:41', '2024-06-18 16:19:41'),
(3217, 314, 80, NULL, 5, NULL, 'If you are thinking about purchasing a Japanese Maple then don\'t hesitate from buying one from Meadowlark Gardens. They have quality trees at a real fair price, the staff are top notch and very knowledgeable. I\'ve purchased a couple and they are absolutely beautiful. I just received another one, this time I got Fukinagashi, and it\'s incredible.', 'quality', 5, 5, 5, NULL, NULL, '[]', 1, 0, 'approved', '2024-06-18 16:19:41', '2024-06-18 16:19:41'),
